4 年 1 月 18 日在欧文广场表演。图片来源：Sirius XM" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Green-Day-performing-at-Irving-Plaza-on-January-18-2024.-Credit-Sirius-XM-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>昨晚（1 月 18 日星期四）在纽约举行的亲密专辑发布会上首次现场表演了最新单曲《One-Eyed Bastard》——这场演出也大量采用了他们的经典专辑《Dookie》和《Dookie》中的素材。 &#39;美国白痴&#39;。查看下面的片段和歌单。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737"><b>绿日乐队 - 《救世主》评论：自《美国白痴》以来他们最好的作品</b></a></li></ul><p>这些流行朋克老将登上位于市中心可容纳 1,500 人的欧文广场 (Irving Plaza) 的舞台，庆祝他们的第 14 张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">Saviors</a> 》的发行，这是<a href="https://www.siriusxm.com/small-stage-series" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sirius XM 小舞台系列</a>的一部分。</p><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-confirm-theyll-be-playing-dookie-and-american-idiot-in-full-on-2024-saviors-world-tour-3572429">本周确认他们将在即将到来的 2024 年“Saviors”巡演中完整演奏“Dookie”和“American Idiot”后</a>，三人组通过一组充满来自两张唱片以及他们的新唱片。</p><p>乐队以《American Idiot》拉开序幕，接着演奏《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-green-day-debut-new-song-look-ma-no-brains-at-when-we-were-young-2023-3519774">Look Ma, No Brains!》</a> 》和新专辑中的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-debut-new-song-the-american-dream-is-killing-me-at-las-vegas-club-show-watch-footage-setlist-3518534">美国梦正在杀死我</a>》，然后首次现场演奏《独眼混蛋》。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@xxclandestinexx/video/7325622380758404394" data-video-id="7325622380758404394" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section> <a target="_blank" title="@xxclandestinexx" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@xxclandestinexx?refer=embed">@xxclandestinexx</a></p><p> Green Day One Eyed Bastard 现场首秀 Tiny Club Show Irving Plaza NYC 01/18/24 <a title="绿日" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/greenday?refer=embed">#greenday</a> <a title="绿日现场" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/greendaylive?refer=embed">#greendaylive</a> <a title="现场音乐" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/livemusic?refer=embed">#livemusic</a> <a title="音乐会" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/concert?refer=embed">#concert</a> <a title="90年代" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/90s?refer=embed">#90s</a> <a title="音乐" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/music?refer=embed">#music</a> <a title="比利乔阿姆斯特朗" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/billiejoearmstrong?refer=embed">#billiejoearmstrong</a> <a title="纽约" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/nyc?refer=embed">#nyc</a> <a title="纽约" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/ny?refer=embed">#ny</a> <a title="纽约市" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/newyorkcity?refer=embed">#newyorkcity</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 克里斯" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7325622527449910058?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – 克里斯</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagr