新证据表明《大金刚之王》并没有为了获得高分而作弊https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-evidence-suggests-king-of-donkey-kong-didnt-cheat-to-achieve-high-scores-3573778?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=新证据表明驴王并没有通过作弊获得高分Ali ShutlerFri, 19 Jan 2024 14:40:46 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3573778 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="人们在玩“大金刚”街机游戏" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>显然，比利·米切尔的记录尝试中的不一致可能是由硬件故障引起的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-evidence-suggests-king-of-donkey-kong-didnt-cheat-to-achieve-high-scores-3573778">《新证据表明《大金刚之王》没有作弊以获得高分》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="人们在玩“大金刚”街机游戏" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Donkey-Kong-arcade-game-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>比利·米切尔，又名“<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/donkey-kong"><em>大金刚</em></a>之王”，在新的证据被分享后，他破纪录的高分又回到了历史书中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-future-of-games-done-quick-why-founder-mike-uyamas-exit-is-on-hold-and-whats-next-3490793">Games Done Quick 的未来：为什么创始人 Mike Uyama 的退出被搁置，以及下一步是什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>2018 年，米切尔的<em>《大金刚》</em>高分成绩遭到一名玩家的质疑，他在 Twin Galaxies 论坛上提供了一系列证据，表明米切尔使用模拟器打破了记录，而不是使用未经修改的官方硬件这通常是保持公平所必需的。</p><p>经过“独立调查”，他的高分被从视频游戏数据库 Twin Galaxies 和吉尼斯世界纪录中删除，尽管后者在 2020 年推翻了这一决定<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/gaming-news/king-of-donkey-kong-billy-mitchell-accused-of-cheating-by-forensic-analyst-3307701">。法医分析人士还指责他在 2022 年作弊</a>，但米切尔一直在与从那时起就受到指责。</p><p> 2022年，他声称法律斗争的压力导致他患有疝气和心房颤动。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比利·米切尔 (Billy Mitchell) 的 1,047,500 分大金刚游戏！" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VQkrjB4FW14?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>然而，来自世界第一大学游戏项目创始人迈克尔·齐达博士的新证据似乎证明米切尔是无辜的。这份长达两页的<a href="https://mikezyda.com/resources/Press/2024.01.15-ZydaExpertReportFinal.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文件</a>[通过<a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/after-a-6-year-brawl-billy-mitchell-is-back-in-the-record-books-even-though-twin-galaxies-had-all-its-ducks-in-a-row-for-a-courtroom-showdown/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>PCGamer</em></a> ] 表示，米切尔破纪录的尝试中报告的可疑异常可能会发生在未经修改的<em>大金刚</em>街机硬件上，“如果所涉及的硬件可能由于组件退化而出现故障”。</p><p>因此，双子星系将米切尔的三项<em>大金刚</em>高分恢复到其<a href="https://www.twingalaxies.com/The-Original-TG-Historical-Database">历史数据库</a>中。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比利·米切尔在《大金刚》中获得 1,050,100 分！" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sXb8HzipTso?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “公平考虑 Zyda 博士代表米切尔先生提供的专家意见，并与 Twin Galaxies 致力于细致记录和保存视频游戏得分历史的承诺相一致，Twin Galaxies 迄今为止应恢复 Mitchell 先生的所有得分作为一部分双星系网站上的官方历史数据库，”一份<a href="https://www.twingalaxies.com/feed_details.php/6194/twin-galaxies-statement/5">声明</a>说。双星系还删除了最初指控米切尔作弊的帖子。</p><p>然而，米切尔的分数不会出现在双星系不断更新的<a href="https://www.twingalaxies.com/game/donkey-kong" target="_blank" rel="noopener">记分牌</a>上。</p><p> Twin Galaxies 的律师 David Tashroudian 告诉<a href="https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2024/01/twin-galaxies-lawyer-settlement-with-billy-mitchell-was-a-business-decision/">Ars Technica</a> ，该公司在与 Mitchell 的法律诉讼中“全力以赴”，但“涉及的成本过高，双方都面临很多不确定性”在审判中，他们希望按照自己的条件解决此事。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/obsidian-entertainment">Obsidian Entertainment</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/obsidians-avowed-reveals-flexible-combat-system-and-release-window-in-new-deep-dive-trailer-3573746">对“灵活”战斗系统的深入研究，</a>该系统将在“丰富、怪异和精彩”的 RPG <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/avowed">Avowed</a></em>中呈现。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-evidence-suggests-king-of-donkey-kong-didnt-cheat-to-achieve-high-scores-3573778">《新证据表明《大金刚之王》没有作弊以获得高分》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听德克兰·麦肯纳 (Declan McKenna) 的迷幻新单曲《穆赫兰道的晚餐与美酒》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-declan-mckennas-trippy-single-mulhollands-dinner-and-wine-3573798?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-declan-mckennas-trippy-single-穆赫兰兹晚餐和美酒Max PilleyFri, 19 Jan 2024 14:40:01 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3573798 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德克兰·麦肯纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是他即将推出的第三张专辑《海滩发生了什么？》的最新预告。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-declan-mckennas-trippy-single-mulhollands-dinner-and-wine-3573798">聆听德克兰·麦肯纳 (Declan McKenna) 的迷幻新单曲《穆赫兰道的晚餐和美酒》(Mulholland&#39;s Dining And Wine)</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德克兰·麦肯纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/declan_mckenna_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/declan-mckenna">德克兰·麦肯纳 (Declan McKenna)</a>发行了他即将推出的第三张专辑中的最新单曲《穆赫兰道的晚餐和美酒》——请查看下面的曲目。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="218" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-new-single-sympathy-third-album-tour-2023-3464783"><b>德克兰·麦肯纳 (Declan McKenna) 向我们介绍“赫拉怪异”第三张专辑</b></a></li></ul><p>这是这位创作型歌手的第三张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-announces-new-lp-what-happened-to-the-beach-and-shares-single-nothing-works-3497525">《海滩发生了什么？》</a>之前发行的最新歌曲。 ，将于 2 月 9 日通过他自己的唱片公司 Tomplicated Records 发行（<a href="https://declanmckenna.lnk.to/whttb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。</p><p>这首歌是一首阳光明媚、轻快迷幻的欢快曲，以扭曲、水汪汪的吉他线和麦肯纳的歌声为特色，“<i>我有一间无聊的公寓，还有所有的毒品/我他妈的很危险，我得到了我想要的</i>”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Declan McKenna - 穆赫兰道的晚餐和美酒（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cS4tl6B7lBQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>谈到这首歌时，麦肯纳说道：“《穆赫兰道的晚餐和美酒》是与吉安卢卡·布切拉蒂 (Gianluca Buccellati) 共同创作的，讲述了一个关于卡通犯罪二人组的怪异、扭曲的故事，而该标题的起源来自于《穆赫兰道》的非法许可。英国，但它与洛杉矶的穆赫兰道纠缠在一起。歌词来自于在山上开车时的观察以及在奇怪、时髦的聚会上的谈话。”</p><p>麦肯纳此前曾于 12 月分享过单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-releases-new-single-elevator-hum-listen-3552137">Elevator Hum</a> 》，在此之前还分享过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-announces-new-lp-what-happened-to-the-beach-and-shares-single-nothing-works-3497525">《Nothing Works》</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AniO6LmCq_s">《Sympathy》</a> 。</p><p>谈到这张继 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/declan-mckenna-zeros-album-review-2744095">《Zeros》</a>之后的新专辑，麦肯纳解释道：“在过去的几年里，音乐制作背后有一些分量。我想敞开心扉，不要太担心事情。”</p><p> “过去我只需要稍微降低强度并获得一些乐趣时，我一直对自己施加很大的压力。”</p><p>他继续说：“我总是会用音乐来表达我的想法，但是我们生活在一个我想为以前做出的对话的时代，现在在公开场合更加公开。”</p><p>麦肯纳（McKenna） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-new-single-sympathy-third-album-tour-2023-3464783">在7月对<i>NME</i>讲话时</a>，将他的第三次工作室努力描述为“ Hella Wigre”，“很奇怪，但这并没有通过我试图成为我自己以外的其他任何事情”。</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-announces-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-3508600">这位音乐家将于3月在整个欧洲的进一步约会之前开始英国和爱尔兰的头条新闻巡回演唱会</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/declan-mckenna-tickets/artist/2189205?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=RKUTRgyekxyPW0Hxo00WPWwaUkFS0GV3iX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里找到剩余的门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-declan-mckennas-trippy-single-mulhollands-dinner-and-wine-3573798">收听Declan McKenna的兴奋不已的新单曲“ Mulholland的晚餐和葡萄酒”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
